channel.title: Compiler HELP
channel.description:
I followed Mod Taharok's guide, downloaded jdk6.0, have project 16 as my source, i edited my compiler with his code: @echo off title Compiler "%ProgramFiles%\Java\jdk1.6.0\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java pause
this is the error i get when i run it: Note: stream.java uses or overrides a deprecated API. Note: Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue . . .
